
Global setup:

  Download and install Git -- http://git-scm.com/download
  git config --global user.email wajiii@gmail.com
      

Next steps:

  mkdir shizzup
  cd shizzup
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:wajiii/shizzup.git
  git push origin master
      

Existing Git Repo?

  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:wajiii/shizzup.git
  git push origin master
      

Importing a SVN Repo?

  Click here -- http://github.com/wajiii/shizzup/imports/new 
      

When you're done:

  Continue -- http://github.com/wajiii/shizzup/tree/master


